data.value:
WinLocker is a computer security protection and access control software product. You can use it to lock computer to prevent people from accessing your private documents and resources. When the computer is locked by WinLocker, none can access your documents, browse your computer, or use programs on your computer.
It sports a clean and simplistic layout that allows users to set up the locking process with just a few clicks.
Basically, it proves to be extremely easy to work with this tool, as you don’t need special computer skills to configure the dedicated parameters.
You can lock your desktop by setting up a password. It is not possible to make the application hide the characters of the password while you are typing them, so make your sure the password remains private.
Source Code : https://github.com/SoheilMV/WinLocker
